WorldStage Newsonline– The Initiates Plc. (TIP), a Port Harcourt Nigeria based professional waste management company has confirmed that Dvcf Oil & Gas Plc, a substantial shareholder in the company  had freshly sold another 1000,000 units of its holdings in the company at N0.57 per share  which amounted to N570,000. A notice to the Nigerian Stock Exchange signed today by Olaide Odejobi, Company Secretary, said the transaction took place on September 7, 2020. WorldStage earlier reported that Dvcf Oil & Gas Plc  had consistently been selling its holdings in the company in recent months.